<codeline lineno="54"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="55"><highlight class="comment">In<sp/>this<sp/>example,<sp/>we<sp/>create<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>image<sp/>and<sp/>return<sp/>the<sp/>width<sp/>and<sp/>type<sp/>(image<sp/>format)<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>newly<sp/>created<sp/>image.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="56"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
