<codeline lineno="70"><highlight class="comment">the<sp/>xs:base64Binary<sp/>representation<sp/>of<sp/>a<sp/>plain<sp/>white<sp/>GIF<sp/>image.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="71"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
