<codeline lineno="114"><highlight class="comment">\section<sp/>manipulatin_images<sp/>Manipulating<sp/>Images</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="115"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="116"><highlight class="comment">In<sp/>this<sp/>example,<sp/>we<sp/>first<sp/>download<sp/>an<sp/>image<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>web<sp/>using<sp/>Zorba&apos;s<sp/>http<sp/>client<sp/>and<sp/>then<sp/></highlight></codeline>
