<codeline lineno="135"><highlight class="comment">Then,<sp/>in<sp/>line<sp/>9,<sp/>we<sp/>assign<sp/>&lt;b&gt;$manipulated-image&lt;/b&gt;<sp/>a<sp/>manipulated<sp/>version<sp/>of<sp/>the</highlight></codeline>
