<codeline lineno="171"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="172"><highlight class="comment">In<sp/>this<sp/>example,<sp/>we<sp/>create<sp/>two<sp/>blank<sp/>images,<sp/>paint<sp/>a<sp/>line<sp/>on<sp/>each,<sp/>and<sp/>use<sp/>them<sp/>to<sp/>create<sp/>an<sp/>animated<sp/>gif.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="173"><highlight class="comment"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="174"><highlight class="comment">\code</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="175"><highlight class="comment">import<sp/>module<sp/>namespace<sp/>basic<sp/>=<sp/>&quot;http://www.zorba-xquery.com/modules/image/basic&quot;;</highlight></codeline>
