<codeline lineno="188"><highlight class="comment">Then,<sp/>in<sp/>line<sp/>8,<sp/>we<sp/>return<sp/>the<sp/>output<sp/>of<sp/>anim:create-animated-gif<sp/>(which<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>GIF<sp/>image)<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="189"><highlight class="comment">for<sp/>which<sp/>we<sp/>pass<sp/>the<sp/>images<sp/>from<sp/>lines<sp/>6<sp/>and<sp/>seven<sp/>as<sp/>arguments.<sp/>The<sp/>function<sp/>composes<sp/></highlight></codeline>
